tique-one | Metacritique 1: The Critic's Duty]]]**: From Kalinin, some guiding principles for critique, and discussion about the place critique has in the SCP wiki and its community.<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)## **[[[metacritique-two | Metacritique 2: Anomalous Art]]]**: How to approach depictions of anomalous artists in the Foundation universe.<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)## **[[[things-what-do-a-thing-an-essay-on-things | 'Things what do a thing'- An Essay On Anomalies That Are Things That Do A Thing]]]**: Nico talks about different ways to handle writing the most classic, popular, overused SCP formula. <br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|文章)## **[[[zyn-s-crit-tips-i | Zyn's Crit Tips I: Reviewing Long Drafts]]]**: The Captain of the Forum Crit Team (aka Butterfly Squad) talks about how to power through reviewing long works.<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)## **[[[zyn-s-crit-tips-ii | Zyn's Crit Tips II: Reviewing Overhaul Works]]]**: How to approach drafts that need a lot of revamping without giving you or the author a headache. <br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)## **[[[zyn-s-crit-tips-iii | Zyn's Crit Tips III: The Quick Crit]]]**: How to write helpful critique at a relatively quick pace!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n[[div style=&quot;display: inline-block; border-radius: 10px; border:dashed 1px #444444; background:\t#F5F5F5; float:top; width:96.5%; padding:10px&quot;]]<br />\n<br />\n+ __各種有用的訊息與文章__<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##**[[[/feitag-give-attribution-for-images|關於圖片來源與歸屬的注意事項]]]**：關於圖片需要注意的事情。<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##**[[[/understanding-paragraph|認識段落寫作]]]**：怎麼把描述部分寫得像真正的報告，讓你在創作上增加看起來的專業感，同時也讓讀者更容易理解你的作品。<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##**[[[rating-against-traditions|挑戰傳統評分方式：關於自訂評分模版]]]**：關於自訂評分模版的詳細教學。<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##**[[[template-translation|模板翻譯指南]]]**：翻譯模板的注意事項與教學。<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##**[[[sth-about-translation|翻譯不只是塊蛋糕]]]**：詳細解說了翻譯與翻譯的注意事項的指導文章<br />\n<br />\n* ##43D738|(文章)##